606
00:40:33,599 --> 00:40:35,580
You'll be the death of me.

607
00:40:37,099 --> 00:40:42,959
That said, does Song Yan think the same way you do?

608
00:40:42,959 --> 00:40:45,619
Just now at the police station,

609
00:40:45,619 --> 00:40:48,079
