00:40:48,079 --> 00:40:50,079
Your mother and brother don't like him.

611
00:40:50,079 --> 00:40:52,150
I'm sure he knows.

612
00:40:52,150 --> 00:40:54,855
Today, he got another reality check from your brother.

613
00:40:54,855 --> 00:40:56,854
He's such a proud man.

614
00:40:56,854 --> 00:40:59,280
That couldn't have felt good for him.

